OOC: Airly... the bamphomet thing slashed at Blacky like a dozen 
times heh. Might want to post for that and the huge beam of 
chaochitan energy heading towards her. Although its only her 
simulated body...


Vampiza tilts his head to the side at Windlords words. They made 
absolutely no sense at all... Luckily for Windlord this put Vampiza 
off gaurd and all 25 shots hit him creating wounds in various parts 
of his body. The wounds and pain made Vampiza come back to reality 
and then he unleashed a beam of Choachitan energy at him and then one 
at Cleder.

Meanwhile... at the Oblivion, Frostbite nods and opens a comm to 
Zardus seeing as how he's the only one left and she is the only 
Infecticon to have a comm system naturally.

Frostbite: "That will do. I shall meet you there."

Frostbite then stood and pressed a button causing the Oblivion to 
dissapear from sight beneath the water. She then headed off for the 
hangar.

Still meanwhile... at the second Infecticon base, Blight laughs a bit 
as he responds to Alectos transmission.

Blight: "Very well... come on in... your going to like it down here. 
Down here we all float..."(couldnt resist putting that in I was 
watching "It" like last week on Scifi channel... or was it tuesday? 
damn this mind of mine.)

with that the vortex opened up again, this time just enough for 
Alecto to fly through it.
